<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fcf9f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .card { max-width: 500px; background: #ffffff; margin: 0 auto; padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #eaeaea; text-align: center; }
        h1 { color: #111111; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { color: #555555; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .promo-code { display: inline-block; background: #fdf8f2; border: 1px dashed #c89b63; color: #c89b63; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
    <h1>Welcome to StayVista!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for subscribing to our newsletter. You are now part of our exclusive travel club!</p>
    <p>As a warm welcome, here is your exclusive discount code for your next hotel booking:</p>

    <div class="promo-code">WELCOME10</div>

    <p>We will keep you updated with the best travel deals and the latest offers.</p>
    <div class="footer">© 2026 StayVista. All rights reserved.</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
